Dreams Do Come True!

Our Mission

It is our mission to inspire everyone to believe in themselves by also believing in magic.

We adore our characters and love telling their stories to create magical memories for all.

"You were all AMAZING! Thank you for bringing a classy and excellent act to our show! From start to finish you all did a fine job. I especially appreciated you all staying in character all night and greeting all people with equal respect. That was very noticed. Thank you!"

​-Mayoral Tree Lighting Ceremony

"I cannot put into words how amazing Elsa and Anna were!!! My daughter is going to remember this day forever! She is still smiling ear to ear and continues to watch the videos we took of her and the princesses. Their interaction, staying in character, making her feel so so special, smiling the entire time, and oh my goodness their voices are beautiful!!! Elsa and Anna singing those sounds just made her day even better! They were amazing!!! Just know I will be making comments and ratings wherever I can recommending you and your princesses. Thank you again!!! Your princesses truly made my little girl's birthday so so special!"

-Birthday Party Client
